THE LIVING QUESTION · node TLQ · TLQ · THE LIVING QUESTION · life-science · what is a mind? what is alive? · UD0 / life-science

universe of origin : the conclusion of the minds-without-brains thread
seal               : One thread runs through twenty-three spheres: the suspicion that mind and life are not things you are made of, but things you do — and that they begin far lower, and reach far wider, than we assumed. From a brainless animal to a swarm to a misfolded protein to the first self-copying molecule, this is the map of that thread, the top of its hits, and a look past its edge.
